snippet.title: Proton Pulse Plus VR Trailer
snippet.description:
The Best VR Brick Breaking Arcade Action available on ALL VR platforms!

The entity known as M.O.A.I. has attacked, and the fate of the world is in your hands! Use your paddle to direct the Proton, and destroy the M.O.A.I. core! Will you be able to conquer over 50 levels and defeat M.O.A.I. at his own game?

Available on Playstation VR, Vive, and Oculus.
